379
00:16:38.780 --> 00:16:40.347
No one did.
Where are you going?

380
00:16:40.390 --> 00:16:42.001
It was an accident.

381
00:16:46.179 --> 00:16:47.963
What's going on?

382
00:16:48.007 --> 00:16:48.964
Sorry to pull you out of court.

383
00:16:49.008 --> 00:16:50.792
but the police just executed

384
00:16:50.835 --> 00:16:52.620
