a storage unit in Rafael's name.

385
00:16:52.663 --> 00:16:53.925
What does that mean?

386
00:16:53.969 --> 00:16:55.405
They're looking for something.

387
00:16:55.449 --> 00:16:57.973
Yeah. An accelerant.
I thought

388
00:16:58.017 --> 00:17:00.367
the fire experts didn't find
any accelerant in the barn.

389
00:17:00.410 --> 00:17:02.760
Well. the local fire department
amended their report.

390
00:17:02.804 --> 00:17:04.066
They just got back some labs

391
00:17:04.110 --> 00:17:05.981
that identified traces
of acetone

392
00:17:06.025 --> 00:17:07.113
in samples taken
from the stable.

393
00:17:07.156 --> 00:17:08.679
And let me guess.

394
00:17:08.723 --> 00:17:12.031
They found acetone
in Rafael's storage unit.

395
00:17:12.074 --> 00:17:13.597
Splashes of it on the floor.

396
00:17:13.641 --> 00:17:15.512
As if it was stored
there. and now...

397
00:17:15.556 --> 00:17:17.253
It's gone.

398
00:17:17.297 --> 00:17:19.255
Why'd you leave?
I was killing it in there.

399
00:17:19.299 --> 00:17:21.475
Yes. you were.
Great opening.

400
00:17:21.518 --> 00:17:24.391
And now you're gonna have
to make the jury forget it.

401
00:17:24.434 --> 00:17:26.001
What are you talking about?

402
00:17:26.045 --> 00:17:27.829
Well. you told 'em
the fire was an accident.

403
00:17:27.872 --> 00:17:31.050
but now the prosecution
has proof that it was arson.

404
00:17:33.356 --> 00:17:36.055
And our whole defense
just went up in flames.

405
00:17:45.064 --> 00:17:47.675
So. why did they find acetone
residue in your storage unit?

406
00:17:47.718 --> 00:17:50.591
My ex used to leave some of her
stuff there from her nail salon.

407
00:17:50.634 --> 00:17:53.246
but I haven't been
to that storage unit in months.

408
00:17:53.289 --> 00:17:57.206
We can't prove that.
Place is self-access.

409
00:17:57.250 --> 00:17:59.252
So. what does
this mean now?

410
00:17:59.295 --> 00:18:00.601
It means that the jury
is gonna have a hard time

411
00:18:00.644 --> 00:18:01.819
seeing you didn't
start that fire.

412
00:18:01.863 --> 00:18:03.125
But I didn't.

413
00:18:06.433 --> 00:18:08.435
You don't believe me. do you?
Look. it doesn't matter

414
00:18:08.478 --> 00:18:10.045
if I don't believe you.

415
00:18:10.089 --> 00:18:12.743
It matters what we can prove.

416
00:18:12.787 --> 00:18:14.745
That means you don't believe me.
Raf.

417
00:18:14.789 --> 00:18:16.617
And if you don't believe me.
the jury sure as hell won't.

418
00:18:16.660 --> 00:18:17.922
Hey.
I'm going to prison.
aren't I?

419
00:18:17.966 --> 00:18:19.663
We don't know that.
Why did I have

420
00:18:19.707 --> 00:18:21.100
